{"tid":881275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"住慣環海‧東岸 去到台中勁唔習慣","createTime":"2018-10-29T10:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T18:44:24.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fed261f527e6f850714db9082ae3ae647aefa436","tid":881275,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:14:41.000Z","msg":"中南部傳統透天地坪大，每戶臥室都擁有獨立衛浴並不難，而且空間寬敞，甚至等同於台北3~5坪的單人房。近期臉書社團《房地產討論區》，房仲天外飛來一筆PO了一則「這麼大的衛浴要怎麼介紹阿」，沒想到引發網友熱烈討論，吸引超過上百則留言。《蘋果》就去實測看看，中南部一間普通的老透天，衛浴能有多大。<br />\n<br />\n這間位在台中市北屯老透天，地坪約33坪、建坪約77坪，室內戶戶全套房，每間衛浴都非常開闊。《蘋果》隨機挑選其中一間衛浴，看起來超寬敞，實際拿皮尺一量，衛浴長度約360公分、寬度約240公分，換算將近3坪面積，真的非常「遼闊」，可能也跟都會區單身小雅房相差無幾。<br />\n<br />\n中信房屋幸福團隊科博館店唐政駿強調說：「這物件沒有增違建，一切都是原本使用空間，對比目前新式住宅衛浴都規劃1.2~1.5坪上下，老透天衛浴實在大了許多，也是老屋賣點之一，建議可以再擺進浴缸、櫃體等。」<br />\n難怪這篇PO文一出，馬上有網友建議「 適合一個班一起洗戰鬥澡」；「可以改室內游泳池」；「可以放張水床洗澡」。不過實際上一個人在這上廁所，是真的有點空虛，對於台北人來說，應該也很難理解衛浴為什麼要這麼大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20181029/1454994/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20181029%2F1454994%2F&d=KTBDpI4eu99qGD55MLZpZpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=ae8f9e6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20181029%2F1454994%2F&h=86437100\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20181029/1454994/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181029/640_4140c9034223ffe0bbcc56127e1719fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181029%2F640_4140c9034223ffe0bbcc56127e1719fe.jpg&h=bda67342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181029/640_2e4b40bef9fbb9347ecb4a5659b9fa52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181029%2F640_2e4b40bef9fbb9347ecb4a5659b9fa52.jpg&h=3e6d939c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181029/640_b5521ea8c34274cf438066edf827e487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181029%2F640_b5521ea8c34274cf438066edf827e487.jpg&h=b0686272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太大有乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaeb6faecbf5444ea2b823fc1229537fc8c413d","tid":881275,"uid":33907,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"咪係 清潔咁煩<br />\n都係得162呎嘅屋好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542b76c6fb9a00fc67a84478a0f486e1d5e1390d","tid":881275,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:30:38.000Z","msg":"慣咗坐喺屎塔上沖涼嘅公屋撚應該唔慣"},{"pid":"27cd13b75ea992f40f6f3dafd3a07b54f2b95743","tid":881275,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"廁所仲大過間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0b40611a948f85d498b4bd5fc0ea82b68415cf","tid":881275,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532a2bdf57dcf136dbb6115b27bb95f88bdc4234","tid":881275,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d738590968c956ded148a5f50d8874c753d7c0a","tid":881275,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"整浴缸＋企缸都冇左一半位啦"},{"pid":"e32515435de58e90248e1131424f7670dfea8410","tid":881275,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T18:37:47.000Z","msg":"廁所隨時已經等於香港啲屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fab7061ec759e969f6422948f11dc6a22d2ca3","tid":881275,"uid":525